{"tid":1440862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[禮貌] 唔好因為細微事而失民心","createTime":"2019-08-10T14:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T14:37:17.000Z","uid":69777,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"60aa68e8b6b541b20f543a99cc88910239862ac8","tid":1440862,"uid":69777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:05:45.000Z","msg":"3年黎第一次出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日同朋友係尖沙咀食完飯<br />\n大約2015搭地鐵由尖沙咀上車<br />\n見到好多手足開始搭車去轉場<br />\n好多市民見到黑衫開始有少少驚/緊張<br />\n雖然亦都有人話&quot;班後生仔好咩好驚姐&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到經過油麻地站 <br />\n有個手足好大聲嗌&quot;落車&quot;<br />\n其實乘客又嚇親左<br />\n<br />\n早幾日都聽到人講話8月5罷工個日<br />\n有人都唔敢去出街醫院覆診<br />\n有啲人仲要誇區覆診 (因為佢要去受傷地區嘅醫院）<br />\n所以都要諗下有無其他方法減少阻到人<br />\n<br />\n所以你地記住最緊要<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有禮貌</span></strong></span><br />\n知道大家緊張 但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">講野要溫柔 細聲</span></strong></span><br />\n得閒同旁邊市民講句 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好意思</strong></span></span><br />\n隨時可以得到更多支持<br />\n<br />\n小小建議<br />\nBe humble <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d39fc3ababdee7c91b45e46db7281f092982946","tid":1440862,"uid":69777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:08:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2228aaeb0aee1b195605cfb33dde0ee855b66152","tid":1440862,"uid":69777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:13:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fa632c408b5ba8bf2b3f01e80051fc944a0539db","tid":1440862,"uid":185960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=22e261f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n[文宣］黑白大字報 政權罪行 遍地開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360258</a><br />\n<br />\n文宣就係做比藍絲、港豬<br />\n做比自己人睇有撚用！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bdbc7f1a07dbf40f5b89dcc22ef019897718ae","tid":1440862,"uid":118472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:14:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"95f4084760ab2e1886cd2e2ad5d1720ee0a5209f","tid":1440862,"uid":5063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:15:05.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72353f4c11e497cbfb1e58b91ca0a18e888ab86","tid":1440862,"uid":60563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:16:50.000Z","msg":"奈何真係好多人唔太冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e5d7bf703bc5baae0b20c83b224c76759c88ba","tid":1440862,"uid":69777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:23:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ceb60e2a42434246acd3aaca91016c0d0d0b7a63","tid":1440862,"uid":12334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:26:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a9df06a20ea9877b5ca9f8535df500b0193d2591","tid":1440862,"uid":220690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:27:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e74b56bec815747fa79077ae379deddffa0377af","tid":1440862,"uid":69777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}